{"tid":2311003,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［細思極恐］只要政府死都唔訂疫苗就可以禁止香港人出境","createTime":"2020-12-03T16:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T05:08:35.000Z","uid":258784,"like":44,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"71d8b68d00c1dec32df2da9aae8870d70ba6d564","tid":2311003,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:40:30.000Z","msg":"早前就有澳洲的航空公司討論未來要求旅客必須有接種疫苗證明方可登機，此做法將來很有可能成為常態。<br />\n<br />\n反觀林鄭政府自年初以來一直消極處理訂購疫苗一事，至今香港仍未訂購任何一間大廠之疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n問題嚟喇，若果下年第二，三季世界各國恢復通關，但登機者必須出示已經接種疫苗的證明，未能獲得疫苗的香港人變相將被<strong><span class=\"red\">禁止出境</span></strong>，無法前往其他國家。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提，此舉並不會影響高官，富豪以及建制派人士，因為他們會有其辦法取得疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n另外，如香港市民自行訂購疫苗，抵港後亦有機會被政府「徵用」，情況與年初有市民從外國購買武漢肺炎防疫物資被政府徵用相似。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，林鄭只要繼續拖延訂購疫苗就能在無須立任何法例及不影響特權階級的情況下禁止香港普羅市民出境。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KYurg8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKYurg8p.jpg&h=c505b4d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561622-20201124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561622-20201124.htm&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=d422e5be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561622-20201124.htm&h=4753fae4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561622-20201124.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n最後一齊嚟重温下林鄭個得戚樣，佢咁肯定冇移民潮，因為佢知道到時大家唔會出到境？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/feE61Ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfeE61Ae.png&h=f12c0036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2b264380099a5ef21f98b9a19fbc7f3173874c0","tid":2311003,"uid":376274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e57c8d9245530b765ddc3e53094be75d1f39dc7","tid":2311003,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f282d4909e0f2587ff783bee92db5a1b54412c12","tid":2311003,"uid":135400,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:42:43.000Z","msg":"希望誠哥會幫手入d外國疫苗黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b801feeae7b79689c23ba87e457b7b2d21fe690","tid":2311003,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4b5daf5d67df4100fe2d40e6c82331a0760ea6","tid":2311003,"uid":29276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:44:02.000Z","msg":"澳門都訂左英國疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f462ed3c4665d00382cd8a64aee8a2efbb4bf0b4","tid":2311003,"uid":258784,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f282d4909e0f2587ff783bee92db5a1b54412c12","tid":2311003,"uid":135400,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:42:43.000Z","msg":"希望誠哥會幫手入d外國疫苗黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"誠哥之前咁出位，驚唔驚俾政府一個唔該徵用咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6f0c420580725322f796d51b47f5906ed4943f","tid":2311003,"uid":135400,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f462ed3c4665d00382cd8a64aee8a2efbb4bf0b4","tid":2311003,"uid":258784,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f282d4909